   <narrative xml:lang="EN">UTTARAKHAND RELIEF &amp; REHABILITATION</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The heavy rainfall and cloud burst on June 16 &amp; 17, 2013, in the hill town of Kedarnath and the surrounding valley in Uttarakhand, India, causing unprecedented flash floods, has left hundreds dead, destroyed entire villages and roads and affected thousands of people. The next step will be to work for the long-term empowerment and rehabilitation of the affected communities. We plan to get involved in people&apos;s homes and providing skill development training to them.</narrative>
  </description>
